These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 5

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-1::.
There are 2 different nationalities: british, japanese
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: october, january
1. the japanese is somewhere to the left of the person who's birthday is in october##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |
| Nationality           | japanese | british |
| Birthday   | january     | october  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-2::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, classical
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, chinese
1. the pakistani is somewhere to the left of the fan of folk##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |     2     |
| Music-Genre         | classical   | folk      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | chinese |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-3::.
City: prague, rome
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: january, march
1. the person traveling to prague is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in january##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2    |
| City   | rome | prague    |
| Birthday     | january | march |

 #################################

 
