.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-5::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: bellflower, iris
House: farmhouse, art-deco
1. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the right of the art-deco house##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Flower   | iris | bellflower |
| House     | art-deco    | farmhouse    |

