.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-10::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, aristoff
City: hannover, venice
1. the person traveling to venice is somewhere to the left of the person traveling to hannover##5
2. the ritmeester-smoker is somewhere to the right of the aristoff-smoker##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |    2    |
| Cigar   | aristoff | ritmeester |
| City     | venice   | hannover    |

