.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-5-16::.
2 different pets are kept: mouse, horse
House: townhouse, tower
1. the tower house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5
2. the owner of the mouse is on the right of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |
| Pet      | horse        | mouse  |
| House   | tower | townhouse |

